net.viktorc.detroid.framework.engine

Enum MoveSetBase

  • Object
    • Enum<MoveSetBase>
      • MoveSetBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<MoveSetBase>

    public enum MoveSetBase
extends Enum<MoveSetBase>
    An enum of pre-calculated move set databases for each square of a chess board for saving the time costs of calculating move sets on the fly at the price of about 850KB. Each instance contains a so called 'fancy magic move tablebase' for sliding pieces and pre-calculated move sets for all other pieces as well.
    Author:
    Viktor
